        description:
          'We create scalable solutions that adapt to your evolving needs. Our focus on user-centric design and innovative technology empowers you to expand and reach your full potential.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What is the typical project timeline for development and deployment?',
        description:
          "Project timelines can vary based on complexity, but we work efficiently to deliver solutions in a timely manner. We'll provide a detailed estimate during our initial discussions.",
      },
      {
        title: 'Do you provide support for scaling my application as my business grows?',
        description:
          "Absolutely. We offer ongoing support and optimization to ensure your application scales seamlessly and keeps pace with your business's growth.",
      },
      {
        title: 'Do you offer consultation for project ideas and feasibility assessments?',
        description:
          "Yes, we provide consultation services to help refine your project idea and assess its feasibility. We're here to assist you from concept to execution.",
